  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a non-stick pan over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and garlic; sauté until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Deglaze the pan with balsamic vinegar. Allow to simmer for another minute.",
    "Stir in halved cherry tomatoes and salt.",
    "Add spinach, cover pan, reduce heat to low, and cook until wilted, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Season with freshly ground black pepper and serve warm.",
    "Optional: Serve over quinoa or pasta for a complete meal."
  ],
